<Base
  title="How to Find Someone's Email From LinkedIn (Without Breaking Any Rules)"
  description="LinkedIn rarely shows emails directly — but a profile gives you everything needed to derive one: name, company domain, and role. The pattern-plus-verification workflow, finder tools, and the legal lines."
